title: Massacre in the desert
description: Survivors and videos detail Hamas’ terror attack on an Israeli music festival

title: Hamas videos spread across some social media apps
description: Videos published online that Hamas says are its terrorists committing violent acts during the recent attack on Israel have spread across the app X and the messaging app Telegram, with many remaining online for hours and sometimes days.

title: Germany's anti-discrimination agency quits X over anti-minority posts
description: Germany’s Federal Anti-Discrimination Agency said it would close its account on social media platform X, formerly Twitter.
